{"tid":1856442,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【Lihkg】微博: 鄂A0260W\"高官搶口罩事件遭屏蔽    \"蕭亞軒男朋友\"突上熱搜圖和諧","createTime":"2020-02-01T15:27:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T17:37:01.000Z","uid":15696,"like":54,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"5f49b2344bcaf932de0583db40c14376ba61764a","tid":1856442,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:27:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一上微博熱門即刻bye bye    突然勁多人推&quot;蕭亞軒男朋友&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以話中國嘅愚民政策同Lihkg 3毛 係一樣<br />\n<br />\n推埋D on9 嘢轉移焦點   又畀佢成功 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2月1日下午2：30左右，武漢市紅十字會藉用的武漢市國際博覽中心臨時倉庫外，一名男子從國博中心提出一箱3M口罩，放入一輛車牌為鄂A0260W汽車後備箱，司機稱，領取的物資是​​給領導配的。<br />\n<br />\n記者多次追問男子及司機所在單位，司機拒絕回答，男子則徑直進入臨時倉庫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A_FOMCwlrHo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DA_FOMCwlrHo&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXtxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=ceac9328\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A_FOMCwlrHo</a>"},{"pid":"e5cea3cb735c700c526edf8f4d36bf583bd791c8","tid":1856442,"uid":15696,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:28:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sNBUm5W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsNBUm5W.jpg&h=4e3617d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e5cffd21769530c5c3c51aaad392258976a3109a","tid":1856442,"uid":266172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:30:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ddb14a283d8d8a1df8e32b6aa891b5c056b11de1","tid":1856442,"uid":15696,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:32:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0ovh4kq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbna